  %h2 ECRuby - Bringing Ruby to Everyone

  %p Join us on the first Thursday of every month for food, company, and conversation about the  latest topics in the Ruby world, as well as interesting technical presentations on relevant topics.
  %p Whether you're experienced, just starting out, or have never even seen Ruby, we welcome you to our group, to learn and share with others the amazing things that Ruby can do.
  %p Our goal is to promote open-source development and education by using one of the most powerful dynamic languages available.
 
 

  
